11#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtcp_nack_stats.h"
12
13#include "modules/include/module_common_types_public.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17RtcpNackStats::RtcpNackStats()
18 : max_sequence_number_(0), requests_(0), unique_requests_(0) {}
19
20void RtcpNackStats::ReportRequest(uint16_t sequence_number) {
21 if (requests_ == 0 ||
22 IsNewerSequenceNumber(sequence_number, max_sequence_number_)) {
23 max_sequence_number_ = sequence_number;
24 ++unique_requests_;
25 }
26 ++requests_;
27}
28
29} // namespace webrtc
